      "date": "2012-04-03 12:52:57.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.2/x86_64, CentOS release 5.7/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/ab9ba4f2-7d89-11e1-aaf6-525400d2bfa6).  Ran 13 tests.  No failures.",
