        "subject": "LU-1257 utils: add --clear-virgin for tunefs.lustre",
        "message": "LU-1257 utils: add --clear-virgin for tunefs.lustre\n\nSometimes, server registration could be successful on MGS,\nbut the registration RPC returned error because of the MGS\nrevokeing config locks timeout or networking problems, that\nwill cause the server can never be registered properly\nwithout erasing all server configs.\n\nThis patch adds \"--clear-virgin\" for the tunefs.lustre,\nthen user can use it to resolve above problem by clearing\nthe first time registration flags in the local mountdata.\n\nSigned-off-by: Niu Yawei <niu@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: If9e4e56912bbac6eee333c958f191f0d18015f6f\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
